Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>tcl.lang</groupId>
  <artifactId>jtcl</artifactId>
  <version>2.8.0</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'tcl.lang:jtcl:jar:2.8.0'

Apache Ant

<dependency org="tcl.lang" name="jtcl" rev="2.8.0">
  <artifact name="jtcl" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='tcl.lang', module='jtcl', version='2.8.0')
)

Grails

compile 'tcl.lang:jtcl:2.8.0'

Leiningen

[tcl.lang/jtcl "2.8.0"]

SBT

libraryDependencies += "tcl.lang" %% "jtcl" % "2.8.0"
